<META>
title: White Hot Chocolate
tags: sweet hot-drink creamy
active-time: 5min
passive-time: 5min
serves: 1
</META>
<DESCRIPTION>
Creamy white hot chocolate.
</DESCRIPTION>
<NOTES>
Can use half and half instead of whole milk for extra creaminess.
</NOTES>
<INGREDIENTS>
Whole milk: 1 cup
White chocolate: 2 oz, coarsely chopped
Vanilla extract: 1/4 tsp
</INGREDIENTS>
<STEPS>
Combine ingredients in pot over medium heat and whisk until combined and desired temperature is reached.
</STEPS>
